{"tid":1538141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國旅行團在新西蘭遇車禍六死多傷","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:51:06.000Z","uid":33775,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"59aa5719035303d19e56b3eeb4b3efff6e36bdc7","tid":1538141,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:29:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一輛載着中國遊客的旅遊巴在新西蘭北島發生交通意外，六人死亡、多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n現場是著名旅遊城鎮羅托魯阿，警方封鎖現場調查。一輛旅遊巴失控翻側，有目擊者說當時風雨很大。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐新西蘭使館指車上有25人，包括司機和導遊，其餘是遊客，大部分來自四川，事故造成六人死亡，使館已經啟動應急機制。"},{"pid":"1b14e97e51dd022f1d8330b214378e6fe5b4437c","tid":1538141,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"Good..."},{"pid":"edcb01d3df7cdd470d213f953994eeb2f4ee106d","tid":1538141,"uid":9217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:31:00.000Z","msg":"想捐錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俾紐西蘭整返條路"},{"pid":"88f4726e569c6ac69b1c55157bb6283d3fc98ec5","tid":1538141,"uid":46033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:38:53.000Z","msg":"小鳯姐話攰.JPG"},{"pid":"7c3c3bae66261b4cfb85125ac0e3deeb1b769888","tid":1538141,"uid":82373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:41:24.000Z","msg":"好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a1aa4b2217b9537e5c59aeb9d2646339306daa","tid":1538141,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"好慘呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n架旅遊巴無事呀?"},{"pid":"1c03c79684b6076f5de59c5c0a6a8b0f6e8cff59","tid":1538141,"uid":105387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:44:35.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"a9ad0196e8461e6c181ea3dac17d3865e9ccae9c","tid":1538141,"uid":100714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"喜見樂聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f1294f441697